{"tid":1946603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路透社就香港示威第二輪民意調查,支持港獨比例上升","createTime":"2020-03-27T17:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T08:56:59.000Z","uid":283912,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"27cbc3c904900cc0453917eb53f823b5d83e30c5","tid":1946603,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:44:14.000Z","msg":"Tg轉載:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=6d7c4004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社就香港示威作第二輪民意調查，重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻港獨支持度由17%上升至20%，反對率則由68%下降至56%，無意見者由9%上升至18%；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻58%計劃於立法會選舉投票予泛民主派，22%計劃投給建制派，其餘為未決定或不打算投票，比率與上屆區議會選舉結果相若；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻58%受訪者支持反送中運動，28%反對，比率與上次調查相若；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻支持五大訴求的受訪者佔60-70%，反對者佔15%，比率亦與上次調查相若。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-poll/exclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-poll%2Fexclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=948ef93d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-poll%2Fexclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L&h=e4c83381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-poll/exclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞<br />\n<br />\n港共黑警搞咁多輿論戰都係得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511d49c30b1f1eb79f84a9540b76f89b988526fc","tid":1946603,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"話要體制外抗爭果班講到咁撚勁，咁你地幫香港組織到哈馬斯搞獨立運動未？根本反對果班十個有九個都係後面做 KOL 指指點點炸，你地親身落過前線未？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家社會大多數係和理非，你拎 35+ 效果大過勇武以卵擊石好多！你唔拎立會點用權力及特權條例？<br />\n<br />\n點都好，體制內外抗爭係無衝突既。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不應偏廢。香港已經水深火熱之中，仲要鬥應該行邊條路線，根本只要有一絲機會就應該去試去做，先係香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 武力對抗九死一生仲要推人去抗爭，你地先真係含家產人血九大簋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上特別指 henryporter、健吾、熱狗、毓民 呢班含家產，E家香港利益大定你地私怨大，日日掛住起「台」打「大台」？屌晒你地老母。<br />\n<br />\n不分化不割蓆不篤灰"},{"pid":"eef93e175fd368d5716003c810dab4175d5f5cf8","tid":1946603,"uid":204429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"點解得20%咁少 香港人仲味醒呀？"},{"pid":"c8e140e75bf14bf7a19a7682f72e4d8fb5983aad","tid":1946603,"uid":283912,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"eef93e175fd368d5716003c810dab4175d5f5cf8","tid":1946603,"uid":204429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"點解得20%咁少 香港人仲味醒呀？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"好多人可能係覺得唔work多過唔想"},{"pid":"c0d2f8ff41c444693d432f73eae2971b3cb35308","tid":1946603,"uid":168267,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"eef93e175fd368d5716003c810dab4175d5f5cf8","tid":1946603,"uid":204429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"點解得20%咁少 香港人仲味醒呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:52:21.000Z","msg":"所以要睇多啲同溫層外面同做文宣，唔好掛住圍爐同嗌交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣係包括埋教育嗰班「獨立不了但我好憎中共」嘅人，就