usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社就香港示威作第二輪民意調查，重點如下：<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻港獨支持度由17%上升至20%，反對率則由68%下降至56%，無意見者由9%上升至18%；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻58%計劃於立法會選舉投票予泛民主派，22%計劃投給建制派，其餘為未決定或不打算投票，比率與上屆區議會選舉結果相若；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻58%受訪者支持反送中運動，28%反對，比率與上次調查相若；<br />\n<br />\n👉🏻支持五大訴求的受訪者佔60-70%，反對者佔15%，比率亦與上次調查相若。<br />\n<br />\n相關報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-poll/exclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-poll%2Fexclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fr3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=948ef93d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-hongkong-protests-poll%2Fexclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L&h=e4c83381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-hongkong-protests-poll/exclusive-support-for-hong-kong-protesters-demands-rises-even-as-coronavirus-halts-rallies-poll-idUSKBN21E11L</a><br />\n<br />\n#香港新聞<br />\n<br />\n港共黑警搞咁多輿論戰都係得個吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:44:02.000Z","msg":"邊有得個吉<br />\n搞完明明係多人支持港獨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bced4948566cb1fec190242afeae80817be84e0","tid":1946603,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:47:16.000Z","msg":"共狗種撚埋票都唔撚過半<br />\n中聯辦應該搵班傻閪建制照肺"},{"pid":"1a404f45b7fe47fb33dfcba62724520323caac77","tid":1946603,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eef93e175fd368d5716003c810dab4175d5f5cf8","tid":1946603,"uid":204429,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T17:46:19.000Z","msg":"點解得20%咁少 香港人仲味醒呀？"},"c